achments'=>'下載並匯入檔案附件','Import Attachments'=>'匯入附件','If a new user is created by WordPress, a new password will be randomly generated and the new user&#8217;s role will be set as %s. Manually changing the new user&#8217;s details will be necessary.'=>'如果透過 WordPress 建立新使用者，會為這位新使用者隨機產生一組密碼，並將新使用者的使用者角色指派為 <code>%s</code>。手動變更新使用者的詳細資料為匯入操作完成後的必要操作。','To make it simpler for you to edit and save the imported content, you may want to reassign the author of the imported item to an existing user of this site, such as your primary administrator account.'=>'為了讓編輯及儲存匯入的內容更加簡單，網站管理員可以將匯入的項目重新指派給網站上現有的使用者。舉例來說，可以將全部匯入項目指都派給主要的網站管理員帳號。','Assign Authors'=>'指派作者','Failed to import author %s. Their posts will be attributed to the current user.'=>'無法匯入作者「%s」，相關文章會指派給目前進行匯入的使用者。','This WXR file (version %s) may not be supported by this version of the importer. Please consider updating.'=>'目前版本的匯入程式不支援 %s 版的 WXR 檔案，請考慮更新匯入程式以進行匯入。','The export file could not be found at <code>%s</code>. It is likely that this was caused by a permissions problem.'=>'在 <code>%s</code> 找不到資料匯出檔，這通常是由權限問題所造成。','Remember to update the passwords and roles of imported users.'=>'請記得為匯入的使用者變更密碼及使用者角色。','Have fun!'=>'返回 [控制台]','All done.'=>'全部完成。','Sorry, there has been an error.'=>'很抱歉，匯入過程發生錯誤。','User Role'=>'使用者角色','User Logged Out'=>'使用者已登出','User Logged In'=>'使用者已登入','User Auth'=>'使用者驗證','Front Page'=>'首頁','Blog'=>'網誌','Search'=>'搜尋',404=>'404 錯誤','Taxonomy ID'=>'分類法 ID','Custom Post Type ID'=>'自訂文章類型 ID','Page ID'=>'頁面 ID','Post ID'=>'文章 ID','Specific'=>'特定的','Custom Post Types'=>'自訂文章類型','Product Tags'=>'商品標籤','Product Categories'=>'商品分類','Product Archives'=>'商品彙整','Single Product'=>'單項商品','Shop Home'=>'商店首頁','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Single Page'=>'單一頁面','Pages'=>'頁面','Post Tags'=>'文章標籤','Post Categories'=>'文章分類','Single Post'=>'單篇文章','Posts'=>'文章','Basic'=>'基本','Entire Website'=>'整個網站','%s Archive'=>'%s彙整','%s Single'=>'%s 單一','Google Analytics v4'=>'Google Analytics v4','Twitter Username'=>'Twitter 使用者名稱','Facebook App ID'=>'Facebook 應用程式編號','Facebook Page URL'=>'Facebook 專頁網址','OpenGraph Meta Data'=>'OpenGraph 中繼資料','PRO'=>'專業版','Companion'=>'Companion','Instagram'=>'Instagram','Dribbble'=>'Dribbble','LinkedIn'=>'LinkedIn','Facebook'=>'Facebook','https://creativethemes.com'=>'https://creativethemes.com','CreativeThemes'=>'CreativeThemes','This plugin is the companion for the Blocksy theme, it runs and adds its enhacements only if the Blocksy theme is installed and active.'=>'這個外掛是 Blocksy 佈景主題的夥伴，它只有在 Blocksy 佈景己安裝並啟用時才會執行並強化它。','Blocksy Companion'=>'Blocksy Companion']];